    "name": "PhaigeX: Hyperspace Survivors",
    "steam_appid": 2159500,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159500/extras/236d5c7e4f758dffbf08bbdd07268e44.poster.avif?t=1762554884\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159500/extras/236d5c7e4f758dffbf08bbdd07268e44.webm?t=1762554884\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bob, weave, evade, and shoot through a space sector filled to the brim with enemies. The game is built with rushes and high-speed chases in mind, so make full use of your mobility and firepower. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159500/extras/42de7ae8db6bc84c985acad9ccdd2f59.poster.avif?t=1762554884\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159500/extras/42de7ae8db6bc84c985acad9ccdd2f59.webm?t=1762554884\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Encounter hazardous scenarios as you warp around various space sectors. As a newly-listed Confiner, you are to keep the vast space safe and keep rising threats to a manageable level.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159500/extras/66469df9e2a4cba466a72a531bf8322c.poster.avif?t=1762554884\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159500/extras/66469df9e2a4cba466a72a531bf8322c.webm?t=1762554884\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from a variety of ships to pilot, each with its own stats, starting weapons and passive abilities. Upgrade its equipment, and create builds that suit your play style.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159500/extras/b893f6d1131fe6bebf3fa098d8251752.poster.avif?t=1762554884\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159500/extras/b893f6d1131fe6bebf3fa098d8251752.webm?t=1762554884\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The enemy forces build up as time passes, increasing the <strong>Incursion Rate</strong>. As this value rises, new events and dangerous threats enter the fray. Keep this value down by destroying key enemy units to prevent yourself from getting overwhelmed.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159500/extras/1eabced3b1d7d456b9088497bd7e5973.poster.avif?t=1762554884\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159500/extras/1eabced3b1d7d456b9088497bd7e5973.webm?t=1762554884\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Aside from the ship you control, you can summon your <strong>Support Craft</strong> into the field for extra firepower. Not only that, approach it to open up the Support Shop, where you upgrade your ship and use other support actions.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159500/extras/22d42b589fbe10d2cd12d5734beb34fb.poster.avif?t=1762554884\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159500/extras/22d42b589fbe10d2cd12d5734beb34fb.webm?t=1762554884\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You get rewards after a game session, which you can spend unlocking new ships, or customizing your ships even further and making them stronger!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>&quot;Here at PhaigeX Megacorp, we pioneer the latest trends in AI and Warp technologies.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Join our elite team of Confiners to keep our space pathways safe from the rogue AI menace.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>It is our mission to pave the way towards humanity's shining future, whatever it takes.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>So take the leap, and accomplish great achievements together with us!&quot;</i></p>",
